Introduction

Hyeju is a South Korean dancer, rapper, and singer under M25.

On September 8, 2021, Hyeju was revealed as a contestant on the MBC's survival show "My Teenage Girl". During the finale, she ranked fourth place with 210,647.0 votes, thus becoming a member of the girl group CLASS:y. CLASS:y made their debut on May 5, 2022 with the mini album "Class Is Over".
